      • onMonthAnalysis

        public void onMonthAnalysis​(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
        Event handler for the month analysis button. The first lambda expression maps the appointments to their month value, which is then grouped and counted with the stream. The second lambda expression maps each month/count entry to a list where the first element is the month string and the second element is the count string.
        Parameters:
        actionEvent - the event that triggered the method
